{"tid":722244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁繼昌促梁君彥辭去所有上市公司受薪董事職務","createTime":"2018-06-29T10:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T10:14:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b38cc2dd21f09da8ebef7212bb68a800ed77bf5","tid":722244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:14:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1016582&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1016582%26csid%3D261_341&d=p%2Bwgd4HpTMwBOoDtTiDPlJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3fbbb605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1016582&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n梁繼昌促梁君彥辭去所有上市公司受薪董事職務<br />\n<br />\n29.06.2018 17:38<br />\n<br />\n專業議政梁繼昌表示，早前曾去信內務委員會主席李慧琼，提出在內會討論要求立法會主席梁君彥，辭去所有上市公司受薪董事職務，但不獲批准。梁繼昌指，主席有特別憲制地位，如果兼任受薪董事，可能在實質和觀感上，影響公正性。他表示，未來會在議事規則委員會跟進事件。"}]}